        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"action\": \"get_documents_content\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"org_id\": \"{{ $('Fetch Documents Webhook').item.json.org_id }}\",\n    \"category\": \"{{ $('Fetch Documents Webhook').item.json.category || '' }}\",\n    \"document_ids\": {{ JSON.stringify($('Fetch Documents Webhook').item.json.document_ids || []) }}\n  }\n}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-0001-4000-8000-000000000013",
      "name": "Get Documents Content",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [720, 880]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WF4: Document Vault Manager\n\n### Setup - Replace these values in ALL HTTP Request nodes:\n1. `YOUR_APP_URL` - Your app URL (e.g. https://your-app.vercel.app)\n2. `YOUR_WEBHOOK_SECRET` - Your N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET env value\n\n### Two paths:\n\n**Path 1: Extract (triggered on upload)**\nWebhook: POST /get-documents { document_id }\n1. Marks document as 'processing'\n2. Downloads file from Supabase Storage\n3. Extracts text (PDF) and saves to DB\n\n**Path 2: Fetch (called by other workflows)**\nWebhook: POST /fetch-documents\nFetches already-extracted text from DB — no re-download needed.\n\nSingle doc: { mode: 'single', document_id, org_id }\nMultiple docs: { mode: 'list', org_id, category?, document_ids? }\n\n### Extending:\nAdd branches from 'Is PDF?' for DOCX, XLSX, etc.\nAdd AI categorization after extraction.",
        "height": 420,
        "width": 520
      },
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-0001-4000-8000-000000000009",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, -60]
    }
  ],
